column1: I am happy to hear that my friend Jeff Sessions is running to once again serve the people of Alabama in the U.S. Senate. Jeff is a good man a dedicated public servant and an excellent legislator. We need him back in the Senate. #ALSen
I’m excited to be a part of @realdonaldtrump’s Nebraska Victory leadership team for 2020! #Trump2020 #KeepAmericaGreat https://t.co/dWWhEtnByN

Exciting to see @realDonaldTrump announce his reelection campaign with so much energy and enthusiasm tonight! I look forward to continuing our work together to keep our economy strong rebuild the military care for our veterans and reduce government regulations. #Trump2020
